### 👋 About Me

I'm a **Results-driven Azure Data Engineer** with 3+ years of hands-on experience designing, building, and optimizing scalable data pipelines and cloud-native data platforms on **Microsoft Azure**. I specialize in turning messy, high-volume retail data into clean, analytics-ready, decision-grade datasets.

- 🔧 Building ETL/ELT pipelines with **Azure Data Factory**, **Databricks (PySpark)**, and **Synapse Analytics**
- 🏗️ Architecting **medallion (Bronze/Silver/Gold)** data lakes on **ADLS Gen2**
- 📊 Designing **star/snowflake schemas**, SCD Type 1 & 2 models for analytics-ready data marts
- 🔄 Implementing **CDC & watermark-based incremental loads** that cut processing costs
- 🛡️ Embedding **data governance, lineage, and quality frameworks** into every pipeline
- 📈 Shipping **Power BI dashboards** that business stakeholders actually use
- ⚙️ Practicing strong **DevOps**: CI/CD (Azure DevOps), Git, Docker, IaC

> 💡 Currently focused on deepening expertise in real-time streaming (Kafka, Event Hubs) and preparing for the **Microsoft DP-203** certification.

