### 🚀 Featured Projects

#### 📦 [Predictive Sales Forecasting & Demand Planning Platform](#)
End-to-end pipeline aggregating historical sales data from **15+ retail sources** via ADF, with **ARIMA/Prophet/XGBoost** forecasting models and star-schema data marts in Synapse supporting **500M+ rows**. Power BI dashboards used by **50+ stakeholders**, driving a **15% lift in forecast accuracy**.

`Azure Databricks` `Azure ML` `Synapse Analytics` `Python` `PySpark` `Power BI`

#### 🔄 [Retail Data Lake Migration — Hadoop → Azure Data Lake Gen2](#)
Led a petabyte-scale migration from on-prem **Hadoop (HDFS/Hive/MapReduce)** to **ADLS Gen2**, redesigning the architecture around a Bronze/Silver/Gold medallion pattern with Purview-driven governance. Built an automated reconciliation framework achieving **100% post-migration data accuracy** and cut processing costs by **45%**.

`ADLS Gen2` `Databricks` `ADF` `Hive` `Spark` `Azure Purview`

#### 🛡️ [Azure Data Platform — Disaster Recovery & Business Continuity](#)
Designed a full DR architecture with defined **RTO/RPO SLAs**, geo-redundant storage, and PowerShell-automated failover/failback for critical ADF pipelines. Reduced **RTO from 24 hours to 4 hours** with zero data loss incidents post-implementation.

`Azure Backup` `Site Recovery` `ADF` `PowerShell` `CI/CD`

